//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/84/408455.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1356927","time":"2018-6-19 21:09","userId":"sakinin","userName":"三一咲忍","userSign":"","message":"可能也有咬下去后发现挺好吃的shi<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/32/26/322605.jpg","floor":"#3-2","id":"1356968","time":"2018-6-19 23:31","userId":"loannadearc","userName":"巴赫的十二圣咏","userSign":"","message":"你有可能吃的是榴莲，适应了就好吃了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#3-3","id":"1356976","time":"2018-6-19 23:58","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">巴赫的十二圣咏</span> 说: 你有可能吃的是榴莲，适应了就好吃了</q></div>但也可能就是屎。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/26/202676.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1356907","time":"2018-6-19 20:25","userId":"202676","userName":"raaaaa","userSign":"","message":"这种东西完全靠自觉的吧<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">如果有人没看完但是点了“看完”，你也没办法啊<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/04.gif\" smileid=\"43\" alt=\"(bgm27)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/84/408455.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1356928","time":"2018-6-19 21:10","userId":"sakinin","userName":"三一咲忍","userSign":"","message":"那个毕竟是少数，作为一个大数据的统计结果，“弃番而评分”是普遍存在的现象"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/74/37469.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1356908","time":"2018-6-19 20:26","userId":"fantasy","userName":"fantasy","userSign":"(Q, Σ, Γ, δ, q0, Z0, F)","message":"这和谁有选票很相似。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/84/408455.jpg","floor":"#5-1","id":"1356929","time":"2018-6-19 21:11","userId":"sakinin","userName":"三一咲忍","userSign":"","message":"我是觉得弃番也可以“有选票”，毕竟让一部分人弃番了，这部番也有没做好的地方。但是弃番投票权重有所降低可能更合理"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1356915","time":"2018-6-19 20:37","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"(｡´-д-)","message":"其实还有各种各样的问题<br>比如是否要考虑打分人数<br>比如是否要考虑作品受众<br>比如是否要考虑原作质量<br>超级麻烦没办法十全十美<br>虽然我也觉得不应该相同","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1356916","time":"2018-6-19 20:41","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"所以数据上的准确性<br>数据上的客观性<br>还有评分背后的本质性<br><br>三个问题其实没什么必然联系"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/84/408455.jpg","floor":"#6-2","id":"1356930","time":"2018-6-19 21:12","userId":"sakinin","userName":"三一咲忍","userSign":"","message":"评分补完计划<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/42/274258.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1356925","time":"2018-6-19 20:59","userId":"274258","userName":"小鱿鱼","userSign":"","message":"也有看开头很差就弃了不打分的，很难说这些人如果能看完，lostsong还能不能有7分<br>而且如果改成权重不同，都标看过就可以了","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/35/44/354443.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1356934","time":"2018-6-19 21:31","userId":"yinmaoxiong","userName":"银毛熊","userSign":"","message":"以我自己对评分的理解弃番评分不该降权重。评分直接反应的是一部番的风评而不是质量，那么前期弃番的评论分量不该低于看完再评论的分量。对于番剧而言“看完才打分”的潜规则本来就导致了分数出现幸存者偏差，再改算法只会更严重。<br>以前看到一句评论某番的话挺好笑的“XX番最大的缺点就是不喜欢的观众不弃番”，算法一改引号里这话可就全番适用了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/84/408455.jpg","floor":"#8-1","id":"1356936","time":"2018-6-19 21:50","userId":"sakinin","userName":"三一咲忍","userSign":"","message":"有道理<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/42/274258.jpg","floor":"#8-2","id":"1356937","time":"2018-6-19 21:52","userId":"274258","userName":"小鱿鱼","userSign":"","message":"幸存者偏差，学到了，完美解释评分体系最大的问题"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#8-3","id":"1356989","time":"2018-6-20 00:55","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"是啊，洗粉一流〈少女与战车〉"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/84/268422.jpg","floor":"#8-4","id":"1357065","time":"2018-6-20 11:29","userId":"alexio_yorbmapr","userName":"海盗丸子","userSign":"","message":"没看懂，能讲的透彻一点吗？<br>------------------------<br><br>看懂了，谢谢解释<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/35/44/354443.jpg","floor":"#8-5","id":"1357073","time":"2018-6-20 12:03","userId":"yinmaoxiong","userName":"银毛熊","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">宴夜曲</span> 说: 没看懂，能讲的透彻一点吗？</q></div>具体哪句话不懂呢...<br>如果对“评分直接反应的是一部番的风评而不是质量”这句话没异议的话后面的应该不难理解了吧。拿一楼提到的ls为例，看了三集弃评论制作粗糙，剧情蠢子供风格，这算是一种评论，看完后大呼神作算一种评论，前者并不会因为ls后期的反转而消失掉，一旦有相关话题他们还是会说前面不好。既然如此这两种评论都是风评的一部分，分别以两种评论为依据进行产出的评分没有高低贵贱之分。<br>记得之前我在那个谈b站评分的贴子也说过，自己能想象出来的最理想的大众评分网站就是高区分度+高度贴合风评反应，如果对弃番评分降权重上述二者都会下降。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/36/65/366528.jpg","floor":"#8-6","id":"1357264","time":"2018-6-21 11:24","userId":"366528","userName":"花葬红蝶","userSign":"","message":"不喜欢的还不弃？vvv？<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/35/44/354443.jpg","floor":"#8-7","id":"1357276","time":"2018-6-21 11:50","userId":"yinmaoxiong","userName":"银毛熊","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">花葬红蝶</span> 说: 不喜欢的还不弃？vvv？</q></div>不是，其实这话的出处说的那部番我倒是觉得因为风格问题弃番率应该蛮高的，重点是这句式特别百搭啊，所以至今印象深刻<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/32/26/322605.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1356969","time":"2018-6-19 23:32","userId":"loannadearc","userName":"巴赫的十二圣咏","userSign":"(从此再不过昌平)","message":"我觉得楼主说的对，搁置和抛弃的分数应该减半使用，权重比看完的降低一半","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/84/408455.jpg","floor":"#9-1","id":"1356979","time":"2018-6-20 00:06","userId":"sakinin","userName":"三一咲忍","userSign":"","message":"说到减半可能又过于具体了，弃番的理由和看过的集数不同，对作品的了解程度也不同。。总之评分学博大精深（bgm38）"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/05/310594.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1357013","time":"2018-6-20 04:25","userId":"tmpfs","userName":"​","userSign":"","message":"没看完也能如实反映风评。但提供要计算可靠鉴赏评价就得看完了。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/10/1010.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1357015","time":"2018-6-20 07:35","userId":"fireattack","userName":"烈之斩","userSign":"(V1046-R MAHORO)","message":"应该","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/36/39/363974.jpg","floor":"#12","id":"1357040","time":"2018-6-20 09:54","userId":"rumplestilskin","userName":"德罗艾瑞","userSign":"","message":"那还有个更实在的问题，不标第一季直接弃后面的该不该权重更小<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/18/79/187943.jpg","floor":"#13","id":"1357069","time":"2018-6-20 11:56","userId":"ichimatsu","userName":"松野一松","userSign":"(さぁ、世界を掴むぜよ！)","message":"<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">某部番在看到倒数第二三集就弃了实在恶心不想继续糊屎，没有必须看完的强迫追求，那这种情况我点弃番的评价不也是有意义的吗？","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/84/408455.jpg","floor":"#13-1","id":"1357071","time":"2018-6-20 12:00","userId":"sakinin","userName":"三一咲忍","userSign":"","message":"降低权重 不代表 弃番观众的评分无意义 。至于在整部作品哪个位置弃的，对应于多大的权重，真要搞出一套合理的算法，也着实麻烦<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/28/2813.jpg","floor":"#14","id":"1357072","time":"2018-6-20 12:00","userId":"ruocaled","userName":"若卡","userSign":"(✨️VIP 8✨️)","message":"<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">云玩家是否应该和真玩家评分占有一样的权重？</span><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/84/268422.jpg","floor":"#14-1","id":"1357083","time":"2018-6-20 13:12","userId":"alexio_yorbmapr","userName":"海盗丸子","userSign":"","message":"高仿赝品级的云玩家可以，对于非高仿的云玩家，看算法的打击面够不够大"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/84/268422.jpg","floor":"#15","id":"1357080","time":"2018-6-20 12:54","userId":"alexio_yorbmapr","userName":"海盗丸子","userSign":"(影山浩宣唱OP，高桥洋子唱ED，这是毕生梦想，也是永远的梦想 ...)","message":"这个得请教一些搞数据学的人来回答。<br><br>就我个人来说，把弃番人数算进总评分里，是对观众有利的评分；不算进来，是对制作方有利的评分。<br>观众需要看到一个全面的评析，理智的，不理智的，纯粹跟风的，水军入侵的，评着玩的，人气评委的，大家评委的，收了钱的评委的，这样才能明白大体上是一个什么样的情况；制作方需要销量，需要票房，往往很难容忍差评，无论这个差评是以何种形式出现，包括观众中途退场/放弃。<br><br>而且要明白一点的是，弃番的人的行为往往带有一定的情绪化色彩，他们可能会留名，但很有可能不去评分，如果以100分为满分，60分为勉强可以看的水准，不妨把没有评分的弃番人士的心理预估评分定位在50分，即“连勉强自己都看不下去的片子”，无论它是因为什么而弃番。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/06/73/67314.jpg","floor":"#16","id":"1357159","time":"2018-6-20 22:41","userId":"tyang","userName":"星宫草莓","userSign":"(紫玉成煙，白花飛蝶。)","message":"已经弃番了，说明这部片在他心中已经盖棺定论，也不会再去看了，这时候的打分就是最终评价，如果一定要按“看完”和“没看完”来区分，那弃番也应该是“看完”，当然应该享有同样的权重。<br>反而我觉得“在看”“想看”“搁置”的评分应该降低权重甚至不计算。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/22/2218.jpg","floor":"#17","id":"1357167","time":"2018-6-20 23:40","userId":"tlon","userName":"Nanafumi_bot","userSign":"(しんせいもてもておうこくにいきたい ...)","message":"没看完给低分你们觉得不能忍，比起说是希望评分公平，倒不如说是想满足自己厨心理。<br>按这逻辑，在看打高分的也得降个权以示公允。<br><br>这些本来就是动态平衡的，大环境里所有条目面临的状况也相似，评分规则一样，有厨又有黑，所以最终的条目定位不会太离谱。<br>剥离环境只看一个条目的分数，几分算高几分算低呢？","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/82/18215.jpg","floor":"#18","id":"1357174","time":"2018-6-21 00:36","userId":"utar","userName":"塔塔塔","userSign":"(害)","message":"那么如果有了权重，是否会有人为了让自己更强烈地影响评分而故意选择“看过”呢<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/37/52/375255.jpg","floor":"#18-1","id":"1371492","time":"2018-8-1 20:27","userId":"tokibashou","userName":"ウルズ","userSign":"","message":"这种人一般会打1星"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/20/342058.jpg","floor":"#19","id":"1357197","time":"2018-6-21 07:17","userId":"342058","userName":"蓬莱山夏娜","userSign":"(看番是享受，是娱乐，是自由，而不是争吵 ... ... ... ... . ...)","message":"所以还是学我，自己选的番跪着也要看完多好<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">[quote][/quote]","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/86/348699.jpg","floor":"#20","id":"1357256","time":"2018-6-21 11:13","userId":"348699","userName":"告辞","userSign":"","message":"厨子、粉丝再烂的片都能看完，让他们的评分权重偏高于弃番用户岂不是让评分虚高，坑更多的人补这烂番？优秀的作品应该让人一直保持继续看的欲望","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/36/65/366528.jpg","floor":"#21","id":"1357271","time":"2018-6-21 11:31","userId":"366528","userName":"花葬红蝶","userSign":"(动漫达利特)","message":"可行性不大，除非每部动画都有自己专门的评分计算方式，因为爆点位置不一样。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/84/408455.jpg","floor":"#22","id":"1357306","time":"2018-6-21 12:53","userId":"sakinin","userName":"三一咲忍","userSign":"(邦邦人)","message":"弃番评分和看完评分有一样的权重的合理性，个人比较同意#8的观点。<br>对比ann各动画的算数平均和加权平均的评分后，确实感觉加权平均明显弱化了区分度。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/13/281315.jpg","floor":"#23","id":"1357746","time":"2018-6-23 13:03","userId":"soranomethod","userName":"神户小德","userSign":"(夏の終焉り)","message":"弃番的我想打0分，但是bgm没有这个选项，于是我只好不打分了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/37/45/374506.jpg","floor":"#24","id":"1371502","time":"2018-8-1 20:59","userId":"gqx","userName":"Shinobu Cartelet","userSign":"","message":"我觉得应该限制每种分数的比率。比如10分不能超过10%之类的","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/84/408455.jpg","floor":"#24-1","id":"1497310","time":"2019-9-22 10:21","userId":"sakinin","userName":"三一咲忍","userSign":"","message":"涨停还行"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/32/26/322605.jpg","floor":"#25","id":"1373059","time":"2018-8-8 01:06","userId":"loannadearc","userName":"巴赫的十二圣咏","userSign":"(从此再不过昌平)","message":"我自己的话，看到一半放弃的会给分，看了三集放弃的我不打分","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/icon.jpg","floor":"#26","id":"1542877","time":"2019-12-28 16:24","userId":"202975","userName":"Tionish","userSign":"(看剧就是图一乐，无论是神作还是狗屎，你的生活的不会有任 ...)","message":"首先，应该界定评分是对作品的整体评价还是部分评价。<br>从现行的功能上来看，貌似两者是不加区分的。<br><br>那么，弃番、搁置甚至未评分是否包含了对(整个)作品评价的信息？<br>显然是有的。<br><br>最后，可以肯定的是，简单的平均是不能够反应这部分信息(弃番、搁置、未评分)的。<br>因为这里涉及了missing, censored, dropout等概念。要想比较客观的刻画这样的信息是有些复杂的。","sub":[]}]